Open Tuner X and click the three lines at the top-left corner:

Screenshot 2025-01-13 1646541916√ó1004 31.4 KB

After that a window will pop up like this: (click ‚ÄúProfile‚Äù)

Screenshot 2025-01-13 1647021916√ó1005 105 KB

Now the ‚ÄúProfile‚Äù menu will open, you need to click the Licence you want to assign a team number to and below you have a place to set a team number and click ‚ÄúAssign Team‚Äù.

Screenshot 2025-01-13 1647111912√ó1003 43.2 KB

If you have any more questions, let me know!
